node.title: Roxby Downs teenager dies after being hit by jet ski
node.alt: Shot of the river taking up two-thirds of the width of image, with brown vegetation to the left and a loch in the distance
node.description: A teenage boy has died after being struckÂ by a jet ski in South Australia's Riverland today.
node.content: ["A teenage boy has died after being struck\u00a0by a jet ski in South Australia's Riverland today.", "Emergency services were called to the Murray River at Murbko, near Blanchetown, around 2:20pm on Thursday after a jet ski struck\u00a0two young swimmers.", "A 14-year-old Roxby Downs boy was pulled from the water unconscious but later died at the scene.", "Meanwhile, a\u00a0younger child, who was with the boy, received minor injuries and was taken to hospital as a precaution.", "The rider of the jet ski, a 43-year-old Hindmarsh Island man, has been assisting\u00a0police.", "Police said investigations were continuing\u00a0into the circumstances surrounding the fatality."]
